snippet.title: "Shut Your Mouth!" Judge Silences Amber Heard In Court! (Video)
snippet.description:
Judge Silences Amber Heard In Court After Asking For Repeated Case Dismissal!

✅ SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiKzneRB4I4eTN_bHEqV-gg?sub_confirmation=1

Johnny Depp has gotten himself another win in the ongoing feud between himself and Amber Heard. The win that Johnny secured was that despite Amber’s best efforts, the $50 million lawsuits against her will still goes ahead. Due to court documents obtained by Fox Business, the supposed reason that this suit will go ahead is that the suit is “inherently different” from the earlier UK case, which was about his abuse accusations.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
